query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total, 
       SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as studios,
       SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as one_bedroom,
       SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as two_bedroom,
       MIN(price) as min_price,
       MAX(price) as max_price
FROM properties 
WHERE title LIKE 'Ambassadori Island%';
